body: @fs-eire @shalvamist Do we have good documentation/tutorials we can share?

- How to convert an image into tensor.
- How to make predictions using ort models.

- How to convert an image into tensor.

Great question. perhaps we should introduce some utility functions to do this. I think this is a quite common requirement.

- How to make predictions using ort models.

once the question above is resolved, it's easy to feed the input tensor to ort by `const outputs = await session.run(feeds);`. Code examples can be found in the hello-world projects
